      \times \vr_t</m> has the form
      <me>
        \vr_s \times \vr_t=\langle -\frac{\partial{f}}{\partial{x}},-\frac{\partial{f}}{\partial{y}},1 \rangle
      </me>
	</p>
      </statement>
    </task>
